# E-commerce API - Postman Collection Examples

## Register a New User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "address": "123 Admin Street"
}

###

## Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

## Create Product (requires admin token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4090",
  "price": 2499.99,
  "stockQuantity": 25,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "sku": "LAP-GAMING-001",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/gaming-laptop.jpg"
}

###

## Get All Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

###

## Get Active Products Only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products?active=true

###

## Get Product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

###

## Search Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=laptop

###

## Get Products by Category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category/Electronics

###

## Update Product (requires admin token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop Pro",
  "description": "Updated high-performance gaming laptop",
  "price": 2699.99,
  "stockQuantity": 20,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "sku": "LAP-GAMING-001",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/gaming-laptop-pro.jpg",
  "isActive": true
}

###

## Create Order (requires user token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "shippingAddress": "456 Customer Street, City, State 12345",
  "paymentMethod": "Credit Card",
  "notes": "Please call before delivery"
}

###

## Get My Orders (requires user token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/my-orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

## Get Order by ID (requires user token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

## Get Order by Order Number (requires user token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/number/ORD-20231209-ABCD1234
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

## Get All Orders (requires admin token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

## Update Order Status (requires admin token)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/status?status=CONFIRMED
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

## Cancel Order (requires user token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

## Delete Product (requires admin token)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
